divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my friend ware driving back from work around 11:20pm on route 270 going towards Germantown, went we saw a round, green light, like a fireball falling from the sky,but It appeared to be coming straight down almost like a falling arrow I thought it was a firework but no, my friend was so surprise of what he saw and he ask me if i saw it and i say yes man you are not crazy i saw it too. i put a picture of the area of where we saw it, sorry i did not have to to take a picture of it because it happen to fast for us to react
